<doc docid='voa_4771811' lang='lin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voalingala.com/a/ceni-etie-le-31-mars-mapobanmi-na-beni-butembo-mpe-yumbi/4771811.html' term='ebola'>
CENI etie le 31 mars maponami na Beni, Butembo mpe Yumbi
"CENI atie date, le 31 mars 2019 mpo na maponami na Beni, Beni-ville, Butembo mpe Yumbi. Asali mosala na yango ya kobisa manaka. Ba oyo basengeli kobatela kimya mpe kotala makambo ya bokolongono ya nzoto, bakosala mpe mosala na bango," eyebisi VOA Lingala chargé ya Communication ya CENI, Jean-Baptiste Itipo.
Mposo eleki, CENI epusaki maponami ya ba Sénateurs le 14 mars, ya ba gouverneurs mpe vice-gouverneurs le 26 mars mpe elobaki ekotinda ba experts na Beni, Butembo mpe Yumbi mpo na kotala soki ba conditions ekoki.
